STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Michael C. UTTER, Defendant-Movant. M-1108 September Term 2017
080733 Supreme Court of New Jersey. May 4, 2018

ORDER

It is ORDERED that the motion to expand the record is denied. Movant shall electronically serve and file a revised petition for certification and appendix on or before May 25, 2018.
